{"tid":1455192,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[智者入]大專院校罷O方法","createTime":"2019-08-12T08:45:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T14:50:10.000Z","uid":304711,"like":15,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2dd1980a084665bfab51e380a35c4f812b2a8624","tid":1455192,"uid":304711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T08:45:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong>小弟第一次開po屌得細力啲</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家有冇方法可以令大學生同fm集體罷o？<br />\n小弟當年都做過搞手 明白搞ocamp要用好多時間精神 每日爆哂肝咁度橋<br />\n但而家香港嘅社會情況好似唔適合再咁玩 <br />\n唔係想道德綁架 但係而家真係危急存亡之秋 講緊係有手足走咗 有手足俾人打盲咗 <br />\n但眼見而家好多大專院校都仲諗住繼續搞 <br />\n所以有冇智者可以有方法令佢地罷o<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nSorry for p牌仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca23e01d95b3ccb352d553f8b7c8b427d9ff4f66","tid":1455192,"uid":304711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T08:45:51.000Z","msg":"自推為敬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fe6add074430af2ff8c72169e53ae9306ff0318","tid":1455192,"uid":304711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T08:46:04.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"84f46b855b2616aef8851f99a92a607c30417bed","tid":1455192,"uid":304711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T08:46:14.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"e5d5f53c86ffb5f5ef66be9c8ac0e6275486bc96","tid":1455192,"uid":304711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T08:46:24.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"fb0bd2c9d42131402f9a737c5f7e35e51be3d9b3","tid":1455192,"uid":304711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T08:46:34.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"1fa94de99c2d92765a4778d202576049f4cc0718","tid":1455192,"uid":304711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T08:46:44.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"e9011689d5675bd2159889f3881efc0b6ee481e6","tid":1455192,"uid":299446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T08:48:04.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"e4a128f90a4ffd3f85b0c1d8dbf83993c97d5948","tid":1455192,"uid":207713,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T08:49:54.000Z","msg":"做過搞手，覺得好難叫得郁班fm唔去，但講真其實依家咁樣玩ocamp仲恐怖，玩緊city hunt無啦啦衝班狗出黎亂吠真係唔知點算。<br />\n<br />\n營期要一年前就book, ocamp基本上由上莊一刻開始準備，真係無得話取消就取消<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />如果我呢刻仲上緊莊，我一定會話基於安全理由要取消ocamp/簡化ocamp"},{"pid":"2bba12334750b414494c90fb13b593195f1a010c","tid":1455192,"uid":303809,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:29:12.000Z","msg":"無需求就無供應<br />\nfm集體罷O<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可惜好多fm都仲掛住ocamp<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"344bd80accc9ae01097b14495b958911594e8513","tid":1455192,"uid":138862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:56:11.000Z","msg":"有第一個soc行出嚟<br />\n就有第二個和應<br />\n我見我學校啲soc陸陸續續罷緊<br />\n我諗啲soc 好多時既顧慮係錢銀方面<br />\n始終搞camp 好多時每人夾一筆大數出嚟"},{"pid":"4c2b568984cb78039dbaad2a0c9facd563847fc4","tid":1455192,"uid":299468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:50:10.000Z","msg":"我中途出camp<br />\n你都可以"}]}